[This report also made reference to 500 cases of paralytic disease that
were said to be associated with this outbreak of monkeypox. We are unaware
of an association of paralysis with human monkeypox. Perhaps someone
closer to this outbreak who has more experience with the manifestations of
this disease in humans could enlighten us. -Mod.CHC
